        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 13 at 1:25PM MDT until June 13 at 1:45PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 125 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Toston, or 17
miles south of Townsend, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of south
central Broadwater and northern Gallatin Counties.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
